{"tid":2501573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無收窄出入境自由之名 行限制登機之實","createTime":"2021-04-23T12:47:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T14:46:03.000Z","uid":68125,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3e30fd7d63330987bf02cdf5a0a98cf62260c763","tid":2501573,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T12:47:43.000Z","msg":"以下內容轉自K&rsquo;s Aviation <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/495667450636161/posts/1559924037543825/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F495667450636161%2Fposts%2F1559924037543825%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzjk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=dde4047e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/495667450636161/posts/1559924037543825/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbX7vrjUwvixS2swecBsMwHjSmFrBtPv7DqhkE5mAAsym?filename=Mwtshbx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMwtshbx.jpg&h=ebe6a054&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港現時網上熱門話題除153與193外，更影響之深有《入境條例》6A條將大可能於本年8月實施。本專頁作為航天有關專頁，已經早於第一次在香港立法會小組討論二讀時分析過有關條例，可惜到接近第3次小組會議後才開始有媒體關注，至到最近才被大眾注目。<br />\n<br />\n於21/4時香港保安局不點名指《立場新聞》刊登的一篇帖文誤導及失實，並提及香港居民的旅行和出入境自由受《香港基本法》第31條所保障，所有條文均符合《香港基本法》條文，<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">《香港基本法》第31條則為「香港居民有在香港特別行政區境內遷徙的自由，有移居其他國家和地區的自由。香港居民有旅行和出入境的自由。有效旅行證件的持有人，除非受到法律制止，可自由離開香港特別行政區，無需特別批准。」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n但是有細心留意《香港基本法》條文的話，就會發現條文會有特別需要作理由例外處理。除第31條「<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">除非受到法律制止</span></span>」外，第30條也有「除因公共安全和追查刑事犯罪的需要」。<br />\n<br />\n如果之前無在Patreon收看分析的話今次會再分析，首先了解《入境條例》6A條現時爭議點：「(1) 保安局局長可訂立規例&mdash;&mdash; (a) 就向處長提供該等規例指明的、關乎某運輸工具、其乘客或其乘組人員的資料或數據，訂定條文；及 (b) <span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">賦權予處長，指示某運輸工具可或不可運載某 乘客或該運輸工具的某乘組人員</span></span>。」<br />\n<br />\n另外澳門特區早於2020年已經以疫情名義實行出境門檻，<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">澳門居民離澳需要有肺炎陰性報告及澳門健康碼確認方可離境</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n全文已於Patreon公開。<br />\n<br />\nIG : <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/COAfEaJAOvI/?igshid=khmjwpzjenkp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCOAfEaJAOvI%2F%3Figshid%3Dkhmjwpzjenkp&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzjk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=b0e1d811\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCOAfEaJAOvI%2F%3Figshid%3Dkhmjwpzjenkp&h=97135fb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/COAfEaJAOvI/?igshid=khmjwpzjenkp</a><br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n經營艱難，希望大家支持文字工作。<br />\nPatreon :  <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/posts/50378934\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fposts%2F50378934&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzjk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=bf57d43d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/posts/50378934</a>"},{"pid":"7fed97c1c8634d39b322661e9816971812dce23f","tid":2501573,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T12:53:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9a020c838f9e09b227c9594b5fba09311f3f206","tid":2501573,"uid":228955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T12:55:04.000Z","msg":"根本就係驚移民表面上移民好似冇所謂但係背後早咗好多嘢包括人財產知識"},{"pid":"a750b3195374d07103f30ebd7a903632ef3756f1","tid":2501573,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T12:56:47.000Z","msg":"立法前黨政府：冇限制市民出入境自由<br />\n立法後黨政府：依法禁止市民出入境<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6a7fa8060586e4316f677de5ae4549348ef565b","tid":2501573,"uid":392446,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T13:00:35.000Z","msg":"入境前線好黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe0d29c8f92642b115af7b277c0cbb48cd4810a0","tid":2501573,"uid":68125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a750b3195374d07103f30ebd7a903632ef3756f1","tid":2501573,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T12:56:47.000Z","msg":"立法前黨政府：冇限制市民出入境自由<br />\n立法後黨政府：依法禁止市民出入境<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T13:00:38.000Z","msg":"「根據處方資料調查得知，有關市民並不符合登機條件，香港特區《基本法》已經保障香港居民出入境自由，唯特別情況例外bla bla bla」"},{"pid":"ba88a40cefec2b0377df426b1d4b53f4eacbba7b","tid":2501573,"uid":54721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T13:15:45.000Z","msg":"可以出境<br />\n但係唔比登機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18249ba87e29a1026fc3092b0d69c1231e4eeaf3","tid":2501573,"uid":123738,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T13:19:55.000Z","msg":"支那好撚驚人移民<br />\n整定啲野，一唔對路就封囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e02a87f2d436a9e4c19b258a2ee94cb7fd9cfe8a","tid":2501573,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T13:54:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f25b74c13c5962b2e30fdb1497f8c35651ab54d","tid":2501573,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T13:57:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39ace6c33f8597ece36de1bfa8d10c28cb764cae","tid":2501573,"uid":384590,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T13:58:50.000Z","msg":"依個時代講啲黃絲鐘意聽既野都呃到兩餐飯食既"},{"pid":"eefd42da0b809a520b5b53d7fc29b125290dd50e","tid":2501573,"uid":280593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T14:42:02.000Z","msg":"到時就話依法xx"},{"pid":"69fde7a57bedca473ba30a66bdcc15bd022f7a5e","tid":2501573,"uid":324629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eefd42da0b809a520b5b53d7fc29b125290dd50e","tid":2501573,"uid":280593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T14:42:02.000Z","msg":"到時就話依法xx"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T14:43:40.0